'''Shevre'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the midlands of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] eastern continent. [[Mesdri'starn]] was located to the west, [[Rhan'starn]] to the southwest, and [[Sal Vhe'starn]] with [[Fevye'starn]] to the southeast.

